{"tid":1485801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再一次證明香港人係世界級","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T17:53:28.000Z","uid":41045,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dbfa5156b773a13e349e11bc5d0f3babc6618d76","tid":1485801,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:44:29.000Z","msg":"今鋪大家已經進化到連鬼都砌唔到我地生豬肉，要垂住頭咁返狗竇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gJT0fm8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgJT0fm8.png&h=760b1ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西環班狗係度鳩企鳩吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aa9bm29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faa9bm29.jpg&h=a86dd5f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n香港人好波！！！<br />\n但我地仲未贏！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家手足繼續齊上齊落，打倒中共極權！！！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0fb4fc1130643545002e0b54fe5f100e9562b2f5","tid":1485801,"uid":248326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:46:54.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味 rthk32 直播first aid 係西環俾黑警查袋真係嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪full gear 左成日又有鬼都帶唔到風向去中聯辦就要鳩check 人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6347cb7bc20c53028802e4cb9ab2456a9d52ed10","tid":1485801,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb653b1ee24036ea956cced1f2082c2c6af119b1","tid":1485801,"uid":226955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyingshadows%2Fvideos%2F2412061705701511&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3cQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=0ec9704c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyingshadows/videos/2412061705701511</a><br />\n\t<br />\n扮示威者收工返警總</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n記得有巴打講過紅土遊行之後有班示威者行到旺角警署出面，有一個鬼不斷叫在場人士留低，又不斷話「點解要走呀？」之類嘅說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但明明當日冇計劃過任何嘅圍堵行動，我相信宜家金鐘都係一樣情況，都係有班鬼不斷叫人唔好走，宜家共識都係叫走，到呢一刻喺現場仲叫留低嘅人好大機會係鬼<br />\n<br />\n我可能無能力勸到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我只係希望大家可以智勇雙全，理性啲講，宜家仲keep住要留低嘅仲有啲乜嘢目標？我剩係知道今日嘅戰略目標（搶佔國際輿論）已經超標完成，到呢一刻仲要留低對成個運動仲有乜嘢positive effect ？定係比黑警打一身之後仲要聽日報紙頭版就係衝突畫面？求下你地，大家一齊走，好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後話：<br />\n<br />\n今日總結，我認為大家要互相體諒，畢竟大家都冇上帝視角，有各自嘅限制<br />\n<br />\n例如之前呢三個鐘已經去到金鐘同散咗場嘅巴打，因為擔心前線安危，加上今日目標已經達成，冇必要死守，所以叫走，但始終人已經唔係身處現場，冇上帝視角，望住live 仲見到咁多人，自然開始心急，語氣上亦變得唔係太好<br />\n<br />\n同時之間，前線亦想所有人平平安安走曬，自己最後一批先走，咁當然一定會有鬼從中叫人留低/ 賴死唔走，迫你留低「保護」佢哋，同樣前線亦冇上帝視角，難以判斷係手足定係鬼，散嘅速度自然亦會慢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都係呢一句：<br />\n永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bb5df9e4e2a69a801c0dfdf40f1430e026b55b2","tid":1485801,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90689e46ed8f43aa96a810bdf8dd775012aa8b6e","tid":1485801,"uid":263659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6347cb7bc20c53028802e4cb9ab2456a9d52ed10","tid":1485801,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"就讓14億人民到天安門廣場顯示愛國愛黨力量吧!"},{"pid":"85bbd4c2158f9d58e9dea040ba192c6e4e02eb10","tid":1485801,"uid":41045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6347cb7bc20c53028802e4cb9ab2456a9d52ed10","tid":1485801,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"天安門見"},{"pid":"1a7d9b0cb95df95e486c04a21e0a6cbadd15908a","tid":1485801,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94604bec0bd1ff44cf27c7b4ebacf5d32285c3a7","tid":1485801,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席 鬼係捉唔哂</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"2829edf7f20f4c3ec0af3112f58520185ae353de","tid":1485801,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6347cb7bc20c53028802e4cb9ab2456a9d52ed10","tid":1485801,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:48:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"約定你18億人天安門見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b230a4ce0bf08311782d6e24ace78d58c45bc5ff","tid":1485801,"uid":41045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2601034cc7dc7c49b457231476dc02dfff6adaca","tid":1485801,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dis